Package: benfordElectFraud
Title: Use Benford's Law to Test for Fraud in Elections
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jonathan", "Abbamonte", , "jonathan.abbamonte@heritage.org", role = "aut")
    person("Kevin", "Dayaratna", , "kevin.Dayaratna@heritage.org", role = "cre")
Description: Use 2nd digit Benford's Law with any base to test for anomalies in data clustered in 1st digits. 
              Second-digit Benford's Law can be used in testing for potential fraud in elections as well as other applications.
